This is the Debian package of Texinfo, the GNU documentation system.

This package was previously <s>maintained by Ian Jackson, Erick
Branderhorst, Galen Hazelwood, and Josip Rodin</s>. Today, it is 
<s>maintained by the Debian TeX Task Force <debian-tex-maint@lists.debian.org>.</s>

The original source can be found at: http://ftp.gnu.org/gnu/texinfo/

Upstream <s>maintainer: Karl Berry <karl@cs.umb.edu>.</s>

